          skill level only applies to one, i.e. of multiple dimensions
          shall be increased, multiple skill levels must be available.
          Specialties apply as per "original" rules, in particular at
          higher levels, for each skill.  The source for these is
          <em>Harnmaster 3</em>.
        </p>
